pull_request.body:
Fixing failed CI run https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/ci-containers/runs/10530412595:
- clang14 install files no longer available for ubuntu focal ARM image -> update to clang-15
- Fixes to docker tag & push commands

pull_request.title: Bump oqs-sys/liboqs from `a7e1b8a` to `12ad5be`
pull_request.body:
Bumps [oqs-sys/liboqs](https://github.com/Open-Quantum-Safe/liboqs) from `a7e1b8a` to `12ad5be`.
Commits
  • 12ad5be fix: initialize context after reset in ossl_sha3x4 (#1339)
  • 2e42595 Add ntruprime (#1328)
  • See full diff in compare view
